```

Salvar em: `{{paths.docsRoot}}/{{paths.rules}}/{modulo}/{{paths.devPlans}}/{slug}.md`

#### 5. Atualizar Indices e Checkpoint

- Atualizar `{{paths.docsRoot}}/{{paths.rules}}/{modulo}/{{paths.businessRules}}/_index.md` por modulo
- Atualizar checkpoint em `.claude/project-memory/features/{slug}-checkpoint.md`
- Deletar state file de `.claude/project-memory/planning-state/{slug}.json`

